x
2x=\frac{x}{y}-\frac{1}{1-y}.
\frac xy = x\cdot\frac1y
y\neq 0,y\neq 1
y\neq1/2
x
y=1/2
 2x = \frac xy-\frac{1}{1-y}\Leftrightarrow x\cdot\left(2-\frac1y\right) = -\frac1{1-y}\Leftrightarrow x = \frac{y}{(1-y)(1-2y)}. 
2x-\frac{x}{y}=\frac{1}{y-1}
x(2-\frac{1}{y})=\frac{1}{y-1}
x(\frac{2y-1}{y})=\frac{1}{y-1}
x=\frac{y}{(y-1)(2y-1)}
